<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" id="viewportMeta" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="interface.css">
    <title>Colloquium</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="top-bar">Colloquium</div>
    <img src="logo.png" alt="logo" id="logo">
    <div id="welcome-text">
        <h1>Namaste 🙏</h1>
        Hey there, nice to have you at Colloquium. <br>
        In our rooms, you can have your gupshup, chai breaks, brainstorming, or romance with your partner (we don't judge, hehe, and yeah it's peer to peer and encrypted, very private).
    </div>
    <div id="user-form-container">
        <form id="login-form">
            <div id="user-input-container">
                <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="username" class="form-input" autocomplete="off"> <br>
                <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="password" class="form-input" autocomplete="off"> <br>
            </div>
            <button type="button" id="login-button" class="form-button">Login</button>
        </form>
        <div id="status"></div>
        <p id="user-form-bottomtext">
            New here?<a href="/register"> Create an account</a>
        </p>
    </div>
    <div id="filler"></div>
</body>
<script src="/login.js"></script>
</html>